      Constructors in es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util with parameters of type JOctree 
      Constructor and Description
      AdjacencyMap(JOctree octree)
      Here the adjacency between the leafs of the octreee is calculated; two leafs are considered adjacent if the distance between the paralell planes containing their centers is the sum of their resolutions; here the adjacency map is filled using a java implementation.
